name: DISSAPOINTMENT
description:
Worst prototype u will ever play in your life(I dun even test it yet). It is design to make u rage (If u think is too easy just roast me in the comment section).  Only hav one lvl now. If you want to have more toture, you can donate after suffering.

Objective:

  • Avoid touching any obstacle
  •   Don't leave the purple box beside u too far 
  • Also press E to add some force to the box and press 1,2,3,4 to make the box move
  • Touch the cylinder in the end with your box to win the game.
  • if have any bug also roast me in the comment section

The obstacle is just yoink from fall guys xoxo. If you think is good pls tell me in the comment section so i can continue develop the game.
